code: Format: T[N], where N: a valid positive integer
user_input_type:
ch(default) / cnt / slt / mlt / ddw / date / attach
                       ( 'ch' => 'Choice', 'cnt' => ''Botcontinue', 'slt' => 'Single line text', 'mlt' => 'Multi line text', 'ddw' => 'Dropdown', 'date' => 'Date', 'attach' => 'Attach')
priority: Valid values are 1-11. Defualt 1 i.e. heigher
option_interval: Conversation end if this value is present for any option
option_decision: Its empty means conversation end here.
